PrecisOrder (a) accepting the transfer from the Province of Ontario of the administration and control over some 1,016 hectares of land situate in the Township of Chapleau, Ontario, and (b) setting them apart for the use and benefit of the CHAPLEAU CREE BAND OF INDIANS as a reserve to be known as Chapleau Cree Fox Lake Indian Reserve.
